description.p:
In one general aspect of the present disclosure, there is provided a motor, the motor comprising:
a housing;
a stator mounted inside the housing;
a rotor rotatably installed at a center of the stator by a rotation shaft; and
a pulley rotating in association with the rotation shaft, wherein the pulley includes a belt gear coupled by a belt at a periphery, a flange formed at one side of the belt gear to have a diameter greater than that of the belt gear, and a relief groove formed between the belt gear and the flange to distance the belt gear from the flange.
